main event: A resident of North Forestville, Maryland reported sighting an unidentified flying object (UFO) on October 9th, 1968 at approximately 1930 hours.
interesting points: The witness observed the object for approximately 10 minutes, during which time it appeared to hover and maneuver in the sky.
The witness took several photographs of the object, though the quality of the photographs is poor and the object is not clearly visible.
The witness described the object as circular in shape, with a bright, glowing light emanating from it.

The incident could not be definitively identified as a specific known object or phenomenon, and further investigation was not possible due to the limited information and poor quality of the photographic evidence.
There were no radar pickups or other witnesses to corroborate the sighting.
sighted object: a circular object with a bright, glowing light
